# Serve the Apple App Site Association from a non-hidden file — Netlify zip
# deploys drop dot-directories, so /.well-known/ 404s. This rewrite (200, not
# redirect) serves the JSON with the right path for iOS universal links.
/.well-known/apple-app-site-association  /aasa.json  200

# Android App Links: same Netlify dot-dir problem — serve the Digital Asset Links
# file via a 200 rewrite so /.well-known/assetlinks.json resolves as JSON. Pairs
# with app.json's android.intentFilters (autoVerify) so Android auto-opens links.
/.well-known/assetlinks.json  /assetlinks.json  200

# Outreach click tracker: branded localloop.io/for/<slug> links in cold emails
# hit the outreach-click edge function, which logs the click then 302s the human
# to the homepage. Keeps the tracking URL on our own domain (trust) while the
# function does the logging + final redirect.
/for/*  https://wtaefyspddadcrnovumk.supabase.co/functions/v1/outreach-click?s=:splat  302

# Deep-link paths: when the app is installed, iOS Universal Links / Android App
# Links intercept these before the browser. When it isn't, serve a small
# interstitial (200 rewrite, URL preserved) that routes iOS to the App Store and
# points Android users to the test build — instead of dead-ending Android users
# on an iOS-only App Store page.
/event/*         /open.html  200
/garage-sale/*   /open.html  200
/food-truck/*    /open.html  200
